'''Henry Buntwhistle''' was the alias taken by a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] when he booked into the [[Lullaby Motel]]. He was informed that, if he wanted to get in contact with [[Egot Pai-4-Yem]], he was to book into this motel under this assumed name, with a false wife also booking in under the name [[Martha Buntwhistle]].

